data.description: Nestled within the Reminisce subdivision, this captivating Charleston single-style residence graces a serene pond setting, offering a blend of elegance and Southern charm. Spanning three levels, the home greets you with a pair of stately front porches, inviting a sense of grandeur and relaxation. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed layout, perfect for both intimate gatherings and grand entertaining. The formal dining room exudes sophistication, seamlessly flowing into a formal living area. The heart of the home is the expansive family room, where comfort meets style. Designed for the culinary enthusiast, the kitchen is a masterpiece of design and functionality. It features a commanding center island, encouraging guests to mingle in the eat-in kitchen area. The butler'spantry, a bridge between the kitchen and dining room, adds a layer of luxury and convenience. High-end finishes include radiant stainless steel appliances, a built-in microwave, dishwasher, and opulent 42'' cabinets. Granite countertops paired with hardwood floors extend through the kitchen, breakfast area, dining room, butler's pantry, foyer, and powder room, creating a harmonious and luxurious ambiance.   The uppermost floor unveils a versatile bonus room with dual closets, presenting an opportunity for a fourth bedroom or a bespoke space tailored to your desires.   Embrace this exquisite opportunity to own a piece of Summerville's charm, where each detail is meticulously crafted for luxury living.
